{"tid":1633983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要打國際戰線 ≠ 勇武退場！！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:18:07.000Z","uid":224700,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"389b1d7257dd91292fec983988488bb981324782","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"話要和理非到人權法案通過為止嘅<br />\n請諗清楚到底條法案點解會突然處理得咁快<br />\n<br />\n唔係因為你有二百萬人行<br />\n亦唔係因為人鏈或者唱歌<br />\n當然場運動有咁大民意 backing 係因素之一<br />\n但係必需承認<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非活動/單單民意係 show 唔到通過法案嘅迫切性</span></span><br />\n如果唔係2014雨傘期間法案初提出嘅時候就一早過咗啦<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得聽證會講得最多係咩話題？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係警犬濫權濫暴、武力鎮壓、勾結黑幫、打記者打救護<br />\n呢啲冇勇武係換唔翻嚟</span></span><br />\n宜家叫停勇武會發生咩事？<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>俾人一個已經恢復平靜，警暴再冇出現，人道危機已經唔再存在嘅假象，大條道理放軟手腳拖著處理</strong></span></span><br />\n所以除非勇武自己打算休息<br />\n如果唔係我唔會主動叫勇武退場<br />\n<br />\n勇武係需要調整我同意，例如有人講過裝修唔一定要用火，又或者唔使裝咁密；黑裝修紅裝飾藍罷買黃懲罰等等<br />\n但係一定唔係叫停囉好冇<br />\n<br />\n仲有隔離post 都講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">過條法案唔係萬能</span></span>，仲有重重關卡，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過咗都要行政機關肯落手制裁/取消關稅區先至叫有用</span></span>，竟然有人講到通過咗就等於「舒舒服服咁贏」，唔識真係唔好亂講唔該<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">夠啦！唔好再用《香港人權民主法》做籍口叫人散水！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632543</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n為咗一個成效未明嘅法案唔應該自斷雙臂<br />\n所以唔見得勇武叫停有乜好處<br />\n<br />\n至於美國以外嘅其他國家點睇就理撚得佢啦，除咗嘴砲都係嘴砲，當HKHRDA 已經刪去咗和平示威者先可獲簽證嘅要求嘅時候，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英國歐盟呢啲仲譴責緊暴力，叫大家同政府和平對話，唔通你又聽佢講？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdpNx3M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdpNx3M.png&h=3eff388a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地嘅中間派都可以唔使太理會，中間派只會做低成本嘅嘢，最多FB俾兩個句俾嬲講兩句，係唔會出嚟同你行街，尤其宜家已經冇合法遊行集會呢回事<br />\n<br />\n結論：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">能夠對國際施壓嘅係警暴同緊急法</span></span>（Pelosi 唔會因為你唱歌而出 statement 但係會因為蒙面法而出），<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武需要調整但係唔需要停，勇武絕對唔係國際戰線嘅負累，反而突顯國際援助嘅迫切性</span></strong></span>，呢幾日我地需要集中對外宣傳<br />\n<br />\n1. 緊急法有幾獨裁有幾大權<br />\n2. 美國freelance 記者畀狗咬被迫除防毒面罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kennytse77/status/1180841855677652993?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkennytse77%2Fstatus%2F1180841855677652993%3Fs%3D21&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4mzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=b29c8dfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkennytse77%2Fstatus%2F1180841855677652993%3Fs%3D21&h=6afbabf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kennytse77/status/1180841855677652993?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ssataline/status/1180800923590746113?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fssataline%2Fstatus%2F1180800923590746113%3Fs%3D21&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4mzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=9546fbae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fssataline%2Fstatus%2F1180800923590746113%3Fs%3D21&h=c1fdcd3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ssataline/status/1180800923590746113?s=21</a><br />\n3. 蒙面法話就話有豁免但係警犬根本唔撚理<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jeffielam/status/1180866731054518272?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjeffielam%2Fstatus%2F1180866731054518272%3Fs%3D21&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4mzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=1dd5f83e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjeffielam%2Fstatus%2F1180866731054518272%3Fs%3D21&h=ae3cd013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jeffielam/status/1180866731054518272?s=21</a><br />\n4. 班狗見到口罩就9揼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chikit.lam/videos/10156895066779737/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchikit.lam%2Fvideos%2F10156895066779737%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4mzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=6a19da9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chikit.lam/videos/10156895066779737/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thomasvlinge/status/1180844538509828101?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthomasvlinge%2Fstatus%2F1180844538509828101%3Fs%3D21&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4mzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=7dd8ac71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthomasvlinge%2Fstatus%2F1180844538509828101%3Fs%3D21&h=bc587e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thomasvlinge/status/1180844538509828101?s=21</a><br />\n5. 警暴日常 &mdash;- 掉垃圾桶落天橋、搞喊細路女、抽女示威者水<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>和勇合一先可以繼續行落去<br />\n有國際援助唔等於你可以舒舒服服<br />\n世界上冇咁便宜嘅事</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"15d9b8493ea65406463558349353e761f6d57c09","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"想要好睇啲，就擴大和理非比例，唔使叫停勇武！"},{"pid":"2e42c24ceb8805cfdf5f7a45e50a13645c40dec4","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:02:31.000Z","msg":"想要好睇啲，就擴大和理非比例，唔使叫停勇武！"},{"pid":"5cfaffda9e54155b493665b9256da513b51165f1","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:02:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68004d41ea4affcc2f033c9ae3f9b6ff8ba426a0","tid":1633983,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"dd7b2b5fd9800d87a08ba6867c0ecbb5c771bbac","tid":1633983,"uid":78732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1rTwP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1rTwP8.png&h=7db13fe1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59af62cf07067719c124467619e39e8559da72cb","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"HKHRDA 唔係一切"},{"pid":"b2c8dbe3f2bb880d74233da8677424c955071d31","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"HKHRDA 唔係一切"},{"pid":"bac9f8a17a245650da27938aeae52db2ff5b9c33","tid":1633983,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d72093f8ce0aa3979a729b4485490b4155bd1d4","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"HKHRDA 唔係一切"},{"pid":"aa30fb6dd5ec1e025f4b46528c2d771520ff6656","tid":1633983,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ccd959c0191579330b427cb972f693c3e40b21","tid":1633983,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"或者試下咁？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fy6PwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fy6PwF.png&h=ea9a012e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4mzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=3bc033b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a><br />\n<br />\n「戰略」搏一個星期，我地可以贏一世<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630040</a>"},{"pid":"135e877788dc70f7125b92d7573462e3da793ad4","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"宜家叫停勇武會發生咩事？<br />\n就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">俾人一個已經恢復平靜，警暴再冇出現，人道危機已經唔再存在嘅假象，大條道理放軟手腳拖著處理</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1af85d067e5bfd7a76f1323759aff013843363cc","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"宜家叫停勇武會發生咩事？<br />\n就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">俾人一個已經恢復平靜，警暴再冇出現，人道危機已經唔再存在嘅假象，大條道理放軟手腳拖著處理</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d4ec4d852d35994452cd4040110699ea26860c9","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"宜家叫停勇武會發生咩事？<br />\n就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">俾人一個已經恢復平靜，警暴再冇出現，人道危機已經唔再存在嘅假象，大條道理放軟手腳拖著處理</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8cf26ecf18c95a3fde2516baa3ef84d94a56df3b","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:05:47.000Z","msg":"勇武需要調整唔需要停"},{"pid":"ee6dc839ae689b5cd9942545e7654dab962fa6a2","tid":1633983,"uid":224700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"勇武需要調整唔需要停"},{"pid":"a7e62c0a98cab2917c981302ed509d7d85636f22","tid":1633983,"uid":217254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:06: